ike":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"正正經經去睇下醫生啦....上嚟呢度問有咩用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6261adf4961ff69300816f888ede1290e410f122","tid":915973,"uid":40052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:19:17.000Z","msg":"唔好屌樓主住 可能等緊分身家先問"},{"pid":"bfd443db8a175fb3c24ca41a42ba43640cd5fefd","tid":915973,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51bfa7548fffbafa0a834041bfb99c8e384fa84c","tid":915973,"uid":51250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b8a361498b2ce33ac9193b45878672fed015e72","tid":915973,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52671db67b2fd4a5fe42419e9210121e58b26fbe","tid":915973,"uid":1221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"有無曾經中左風 ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"中風係點樣? 佢又冇講過佢中風"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:13:01.000Z","msg":"自己 google 中風"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"一年幾之前已經search過<br />\n咁佢堅持話冇依啲問題<br />\n我仲可以點樣發現<br />\n 嘴歪眼斜<br />\nl           一側或兩側肢體無力、麻木<br />\nl           意識模糊甚至昏迷<br />\nl           言語不清、構音障礙、溝通困難<br />\nl           感覺異常<br />\nl           吞嚥困難、流口水<br />\nl           眩暈、嘔吐、頭痛<br />\nl           步態不穩，運動失調<br />\nl           大小便失禁<br />\nl           視力障礙（複視、視力模糊不清、視野缺失）<br />\nl           抽搐<br />\nl           精神上的改變：情緒冷漠、躁動不安、記憶喪失<br />\n<br />\n以上除左一邊肢體冇力，有頭暈頭痛，其他都唔覺有"},{"pid":"8b83db8556dbe0f483ad33460fc405486a21558f","tid":915973,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a1196d7e24a8b07732d454c7b2941fe54e9ea1e","tid":915973,"uid":34242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:15:10.000Z","msg":"正正經經去睇下醫生啦....上嚟呢度問有咩用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:20:52.000Z","msg":"就係佢話冇問題，book左醫生唔去睇"},{"pid":"6b55d80915a5de1e7ffda8c3f4c26ed4d644379b","tid":915973,"uid":118463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"佢呢種病叫senescence<br />\n好常見 唔洗咁擔心"},{"pid":"24c54180bf4d2f0e24538b136fe76fecb9da63df","tid":915973,"uid":84524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"建議樓主用 FAST 呢個方法推動屋企老人家有冇中風<br />\n<br />\n中風同腦係掉轉嘅，左邊腦中風=右邊身有問題；右腦中風=左邊身有問題<br />\n<br />\nF=face觀察面部表情有冇不對稱or傾斜<br />\n<br />\nA=arm 雙手平舉10秒，觀察手臂是否冇力，or，單邊手臂有傾斜跡象<br />\n<br />\nS= speak 叫佢講嘢，睇下有冇口齒不清<br />\n<br />\nT=Time 如有上述中風跡象, 立即求助"},{"pid":"4958152d48f2dc6d6a20d6a272b1cede1ab6db2e","tid":915973,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b55d80915a5de1e7ffda8c3f4c26ed4d644379b","tid":915973,"uid":118463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:22:37.000Z","msg":"佢呢種病叫senescence<br />\n好常見 唔洗咁擔心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"因為佢仲要日日返工冇休息過，所以又唔似係死頂，中風同伯金遜應該做唔到野?"},{"pid":"90465fbffb913d6495ee22f820ff96502157da28","tid":915973,"uid":29063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24c54180bf4d2f0e24538b136fe76fecb9da63df","tid":915973,"uid":84524,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"建議樓主用 FAST 呢個方法推動屋企老人家有冇中風<br />\n<br />\n中風同腦係掉轉嘅，左邊腦中風=右邊身有問題；右腦中風=左邊身有問題<br />\n<br />\nF=face觀察面部表情有冇不對稱or傾斜<br />\n<br />\nA=arm 雙手平舉10秒，觀察手臂是否冇力，or，單邊手臂有傾斜跡象<br />\n<br />\nS= speak 叫佢講嘢，睇下有冇口齒不清<br />\n<br />\nT=Time 如有上述中風跡象, 立即求助"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/193130_e5602e07147dd60fbbe7032cd8574c71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F193130_e5602e07147dd60fbbe7032cd8574c71.jpg&h=b002289c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09762926a351ccbf936e19e1f5c0ce77170344e6","tid":915973,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:32:18